Feature: User Valid Login
  As a registered user
  I want to be able to sign in to the application
  So that I can access to the user dashboard

  Background:
    Given the login page is displayed

  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials
    When I enter the valid username 'user'
    And I enter the valid password 'pass'
    And I click the 'Sign In' button
    Then I should be able to observe the user dashboard
;
Feature: Complete a Survey
  As a signed-in user
  I want to be able to start and complete a survey
  So that I can submit my responses

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And a sample survey is available on my dashboard

  Scenario: Successfully completing a sample survey
    When I click on the available sample survey
    And I start the survey
    And I type 'llm responding survey' into the response text area
    And I click the 'Next' button
    And I click the 'Next' button again
    Then I should see the message 'Thank you for completing the survey!'
